SHAOLIN TEMPLE

02:35.870 --> 02:37.760
ZEN

02:58.030 --> 03:01.690
Master, how on earth
will you take me in?

03:01.725 --> 03:03.285
I know that the Second Ancestor.

03:03.320 --> 03:05.425
...asked Dharma,
the founder of Buddhism...

03:05.460 --> 03:07.850
...to teach him the doctrine
by breaking his own arm.

03:07.885 --> 03:09.630
Since you're indifferent,
I'll break my leg.

03:09.665 --> 03:11.690
...to show my determination.

03:21.800 --> 03:24.050
- Who are you?
- Amitabha.

03:24.085 --> 03:26.300
Come in with me please.

03:28.170 --> 03:30.650
- What did you say?
- Come in with me please.

03:31.730 --> 03:33.795
- R-really?
- Yes.

03:33.830 --> 03:35.825
I can't believe it.

03:35.860 --> 03:38.380
The God opens his eyes at last.

03:38.630 --> 03:40.965
Abbot, I, Yao Hanwu...

03:41.000 --> 03:44.510
...hope to learn martial arts
in the Shaolin Temple.

03:44.545 --> 03:46.420
Almsgiver...

03:46.900 --> 03:49.870
...it is said that the Buddha
helps the right people.

03:50.600 --> 03:52.310
It is okay.

03:52.370 --> 03:54.440
...if you want to enter
the Shaolin Temple...

03:54.500 --> 03:57.225
...but you must meet three conditions.

03:57.260 --> 03:59.990
- What are the conditions?
- First...

04:00.025 --> 04:02.707
...one is to subdue the material world.

04:02.742 --> 04:05.390
- And be converted to Buddhism.
- Yes.

04:05.425 --> 04:07.480
- I can do that.
- The second.

04:07.515 --> 04:09.325
...is to forget hatred.

04:09.360 --> 04:11.880
...and give up any thought
of revenge...

04:11.915 --> 04:14.365
...and fame and gain
in the world...

04:14.400 --> 04:17.790
...since you're determination
to be converted to Buddhism.

04:17.825 --> 04:19.214
I can just agree to it.

04:19.250 --> 04:21.084
After I learn the martial arts...

04:21.120 --> 04:22.920
...they can do nothing about me.

04:23.290 --> 04:25.820
Okay, I can do that too.

04:25.855 --> 04:28.315
Buddhists don't lie.

04:28.350 --> 04:30.880
Almsgiver, you cannot lie.

04:30.915 --> 04:33.375
...in a Buddhist temple.

04:33.410 --> 04:35.065
The Abbot of the Shaolin Temple.

04:35.100 --> 04:38.430
...can see through me.
I must be careful.

04:38.640 --> 04:40.255
Hmm, yes yes, master.

04:40.290 --> 04:43.345
The third is that all the disciples.

04:43.380 --> 04:46.870
...must comply
with the rules of the temple.

04:47.500 --> 04:49.295
Almsgiver...

04:49.330 --> 04:53.050
- Do you have any objections?
- No! I have none.

04:54.140 --> 04:57.260
His face shows that
he is holding a grudge.

04:57.295 --> 04:59.767
He has to temper himself.

04:59.802 --> 05:02.240
It will not be easy for him.

05:02.275 --> 05:04.910
Okay, you can stay.

05:05.520 --> 05:09.730
Sengman, take the almsgiver
to water the vegetables.

05:09.765 --> 05:11.515
He will receive tonsure.

05:11.550 --> 05:14.620
when he gets used to the life
of an ascetic monk.

05:14.655 --> 05:16.530
Yes, abbot.

05:58.860 --> 06:00.435
No. No no.

06:00.470 --> 06:02.010
No no!

06:06.080 --> 06:08.070
Hey, what's wrong?

06:08.940 --> 06:11.240
Where is my sister?
Where is my sister?

06:12.550 --> 06:14.400
No sister here.

06:18.480 --> 06:20.370
Do you miss your family?

06:20.890 --> 06:22.635
Then go back.

06:22.670 --> 06:24.475
Why must you stay here?

06:24.510 --> 06:27.690
All we have here are
wooden beds and vegetables.

06:28.320 --> 06:29.870
I had a nightmare.

06:30.310 --> 06:32.620
Go to sleep, huh?

06:41.030 --> 06:43.215
Hey, you must have evil thoughts.

06:43.250 --> 06:45.660
Cut your nonsense.
I'll choke you to death.

06:45.695 --> 06:47.005
Who has evil thoughts?

06:47.040 --> 06:49.130
- Tell me. Are you going to tell me?
- I was only joking.

06:49.165 --> 06:51.140
L-let me go. Let me go.

06:51.175 --> 06:52.795
You were joking?

06:52.830 --> 06:55.230
It didn't sound like you were joking.

06:55.520 --> 06:57.345
It's true,
I swear to you.

06:57.380 --> 06:59.170
I'll believe you this time.

07:00.670 --> 07:01.945
Remember...

07:01.980 --> 07:04.820
I won't forgive you next time
you make a joke at me.

07:05.660 --> 07:08.160
- You got it?
- Yes.

07:32.010 --> 07:33.980
They want me to gain strength
by making me.

07:34.015 --> 07:35.910
...carry these two buckets of water.

07:35.945 --> 07:37.875
I want to learn kung fu.

07:37.910 --> 07:41.220
...and this...
this could take forever.

07:43.300 --> 07:44.820
No...

07:45.560 --> 07:47.800
I must figure
something out myself.

07:56.720 --> 07:58.395
Zhishou...

07:58.430 --> 08:00.800
when will you teach me kung fu?

08:01.330 --> 08:03.395
It's not that I wouldn't teach you...

08:03.430 --> 08:06.330
...but the court forbids us
to practice kung fu.

08:06.365 --> 08:08.155
Do me a favor, Zhishou.
You see...

08:08.190 --> 08:11.490
...it's just the two of us here.
No one is from the court.

08:11.525 --> 08:13.610
This...
I am not sure if I can help you...

08:13.645 --> 08:15.475
Hey, Zhishou, don't worry.

08:15.510 --> 08:18.330
You won't teach me for nothing.

08:22.520 --> 08:24.060
Here.

08:25.950 --> 08:28.870
- A token of my gratitude.
- Okay then.

08:32.360 --> 08:34.780
- Huh.
- No no no, here.

08:34.815 --> 08:36.510
Let me do it.

08:39.510 --> 08:41.909
I'll make an exception and teach you.

08:41.945 --> 08:42.595
Great.

08:42.630 --> 08:46.140
I'll teach you for the sake
of your sincerity...

08:46.175 --> 08:48.455
...but you must keep it a secret.

08:48.490 --> 08:50.730
Thank you, Zishou.
Thank you, Zishou.

08:52.020 --> 08:54.290
Hey, watch carefully.

08:59.450 --> 09:02.330
The first skill is
"Carrying the beam with two hands. "

09:03.070 --> 09:06.210
"C-c... Carrying the beam
with two hands. "

09:08.640 --> 09:10.570
- Eh, arms straight.
- Arms straight!

09:10.605 --> 09:12.890
- Knees bent.
- Knees bent!

09:15.390 --> 09:17.780
"Watch the sky from within. "

09:18.250 --> 09:20.280
"Watch the sky from within. "

09:20.315 --> 09:21.870
Look up!

09:23.440 --> 09:25.350
Look up. Up up!

09:25.385 --> 09:27.260
U-up... Oh uh.

09:27.610 --> 09:29.470
Knees bent!

09:34.150 --> 09:36.830
"Having strength all over. "

09:37.490 --> 09:40.710
"Having... Having strength all over. "

09:43.370 --> 09:46.280
Puff your chest out.
Knees bent.

09:49.850 --> 09:52.790
"Breathing out and taking back. "

09:55.920 --> 09:58.050
"Breathing out and taking back. "

10:00.580 --> 10:02.830
Hey, that one's easy.

10:03.670 --> 10:06.550
You know, you can grind
a stone up with your hand.

10:06.585 --> 10:08.885
...once you master the kill.

10:08.920 --> 10:11.250
...of "Having strength all over. "

10:11.285 --> 10:13.430
- Really?
- Yeah.

10:16.480 --> 10:19.880
Zhishou, here are two stones.
Do it with them.

10:22.190 --> 10:24.255
I haven't mastered the skill.

10:24.290 --> 10:27.305
I've reached the ninth level,
one level left.

10:27.340 --> 10:30.375
You are really great.
Zhishou, thank you, thank you.

10:30.410 --> 10:33.410
I'll be grateful to you
for the rest of my life.

10:33.445 --> 10:37.140
Ah, no need.
We were fated to meet.

10:37.820 --> 10:39.460
- So?
- Oh.

10:40.970 --> 10:42.430
Here.

10:43.490 --> 10:45.715
Thank you, thank you, Zishou.

10:45.750 --> 10:48.325
- Thank you, thank you, Zhishou.
- You're welcome.

10:48.360 --> 10:51.360
- Thank you very much.
- Practice hard, okay? Practice hard.

10:51.395 --> 10:52.650
Okay.

10:54.830 --> 10:56.955
"Carrying the beam
with two hands. "

10:56.990 --> 10:59.050
- "Watch the sky from within. "
- Practice seriously and attentively.

10:59.085 --> 11:01.270
Okay.
"Watch the sky. "

11:01.460 --> 11:03.510
"Having strength all over. "

11:03.545 --> 11:05.560
"Having strength all over. "

