- "Breathing out and taking back. "
- Excuse me.

11:28.335 --> 11:32.280
How far to the Shaolin Temple?

11:32.690 --> 11:34.790
Uh, go straight ahead...

11:34.825 --> 11:36.890
...about 10 miles away.

11:37.430 --> 11:39.430
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

